&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;TeamSupport has a variety of tools which lets your team work closely together to solve your customer&apos;s issues.&amp;nbsp; No longer is customer support just about solving a ticket and moving on - It&apos;s about working together, sharing knowledge, and exceeding your customer&apos;s expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;The Water Cooler is an internal social networking tool which lets your team have conversations about customers, their issues, and even your products.&amp;nbsp; It&apos;s a great way to collaborate internally and make sure you leverage the right resources to ensure your customers get fast and accurate resolutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;//www.youtube.com/embed/d7p_AJtk8zs&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TeamSupport&apos;s KnowledgeBase allows you to share knowledge internally and categorize the tickets to better find what you are looking for:&lt;/p&gt;
